// zdoom's default doom lock schema had the keys from heretic in several
// of these next listings for some reason. this file expands on that
// sidenote, why does the zdoom wiki call them "prism keys"?
// it's nice to have a name for them aside from just "key" or "heretic key",
// but I wonder where the name "prism key" came from - it's not in the heretic
// manual I found, nor do the actual in-game pickups call them such

Lock 100 // any key door
{
	// I hate how long this is
	Any { BlueCard ChexBlueCard BlueSkull BlueFlemKey KeyBlue RedCard ChexRedCard RedSkull RedFlemKey KeyGreen YellowCard ChexYellowCard YellowSkull YellowFlemKey KeyYellow }
	Message "Any key will open this door"
	RemoteMessage "Any key will activate this object"
	Mapcolor 128 128 255
}

